description:
We are seeking an experienced Senior Backend Developer (System Developer/Programmer) with a minimum of 5 years of hands-on experience to join our talented team. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in developing and maintaining robust systems, possess excellent problem-solving skills, and thrive in a fast-paced, collaborative environment.

BSc in Computer Science required.

Certification on Data Engineering with Google Cloud Specialization required.



**Desirable skills:**  

Cloud & Web Development, Distributed Systems, Blockchain and Cryptocurrency and Machine Learning & Data Analytics.

Technical Skills -

**Backend Stack:** Go - echo, amqp, pgx, btcd C++ - With Millennium Stack/Cmake Python - FAST api, asyncio Javascript - Node.js with express;

**FrontEnd Stack:** Flutter ReactJs Android - SDK/NDK - Java - C++dfg;

**Databases:** Postgres, MySQL, Firestore, MongoDB, Oracle;

**Cloud Services:** GCP - AppEngine, ComputeEngine, Data pipelining, BigQuery, FirebaseAuth, Firestore, Cloud functions Digital Ocean;

**Others:** Microservices with K8s gRPC, ReST, RabbitMQ Credit card and Bank integrations Exchange integrations (ReST and FIX) Bitcoin transactions and esplora API
